①PE: PSMB6, and TNFAIP3;
②GDM: ATXN3, BARD1, RSPO1, STAMBPL1, and UBE2G2;
③FGR: CCNA2, PSMA7, RSPO3, STAMBPL1, TGFB1, TNFAIP3, and UBE2C;
